ng reliability (conscientiousness), proven stress resilience, and relevant technical skills, with only moderate communication style issues that are less critical than the more severe teamwork or reliability gaps seen in the other candidates.\n**Therefore, I vote for Candidate\u202fB.**\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
